race.comment: HUSTLE (7) resumes and has placed 2/2 fresh, including at Moonee Valley on debut. Has jumped out well at Flemington and draws an inside gate with Meech booked. Suited and looks ready to go. HUGHIE (3) brings two near misses and was a short-priced favourite at St Arnaud last time. Has the speed to manage the awkward and will go close with average luck. LONG LOST FRIEND (8) owns a decent fresh record and was readied wit a trial win so looking for a good return. YOURAWAY (10) is another that has performed well when fresh in the past so is worth keeping safe.
